{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "0.560", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "0.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.960", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Franz Josef Jung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.480", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Karl Theodor zu Guttenberg, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.680", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Thomas de Maizi\u00e8re: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.840", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die R\u00fcckschau auf die Verteidigungsminister der \u00c4ra Merkel weckt Assoziationen von Inkompetenz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.640", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verantwortungslosigkeit und Aktionismus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.320", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die heutige Amtsinhaberin setzt diese Tradition konsequent fort; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.440", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die gleichen Merkmale pr\u00e4gen auch heute den F\u00fchrungsstil im Verteidigungsministerium."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.440", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sogenannte Trendwenden in verschiedenen Bereichen sollen pl\u00f6tzlich daf\u00fcr sorgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.440", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die \u00fcber die Jahre hinweg kaputtgesparte Bundeswehr ihrem grundgesetzlichen Auftrag der Landes- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.640", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und B\u00fcndnisverteidigung wieder gerecht wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es muss endlich damit aufgeh\u00f6rt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.840", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Folgen der langj\u00e4hrigen Vers\u00e4umnisse zu verharmlosen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.040", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt zu vieles, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das dringend angesprochen werden muss."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bericht des Wehrbeauftragten zeigt zwar einige Probleme auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.200", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist aber in derselben Praxisferne gefangen wie die Bundesregierung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.760", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In keinem anderen Bereich wird die jahrzehntelange Vernachl\u00e4ssigung der Bundeswehr so deutlich wie bei der sogenannten Trendwende Material. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.880", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies geht aus dem Bericht \u00fcber die Hauptwaffensysteme nur allzu deutlich hervor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.160", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie zum Beispiel der Zustand der U-Boote, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.720", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von denen kein einziges einsatzbereit ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.240", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erschreckend ist dabei nicht nur der beklagenswerte Zustand des Materials an sich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.800", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch der von Sch\u00f6nf\u00e4rberei gepr\u00e4gte Stil des Berichts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.240", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort hei\u00dft es zum Beispiel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.880", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die materielle Einsatzbereitschaft habe sich verstetigt.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.920", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf gut Deutsch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.520", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gar nichts ist besser geworden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.760", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vieles hat sich hingegen verschlechtert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unzureichende Instandhaltung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Materialm\u00e4ngel und \u00dcberbelastung durch verschiedene Auslandseins\u00e4tze haben zu F\u00e4higkeitsverlusten im Bereich der Landes- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.960", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und B\u00fcndnisverteidigung gef\u00fchrt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eTrain as you fight\u201c als Devise hat sich in diesem Zusammenhang als Wunschdenken erwiesen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.921", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die sogenannte Trendwende Personal macht sich im Alltag der Soldaten kaum bemerkbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.921", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.160", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor dem Hintergrund der steigenden Anzahl von Auslandseins\u00e4tzen und den daraus resultierenden Belastungen wird der dringende Bedarf der Truppe zu wenig ber\u00fccksichtigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine L\u00f6sung scheint in der Ausbringung von neuen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.920", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oftmals hochrangigen Dienstposten zu liegen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.160", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nat\u00fcrlich auch im Ministerium selbst\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.360", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fchrte aber bisher nicht zu einer nachhaltigen Verbesserung der Personalsituation. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.480", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Strategisch betrachtet sollten die geplanten Trendwenden einander komplementieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.481", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ob allerdings mit dem administrativen Wasserkopf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.481", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.482", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der aus der Trendwende Personal resultiert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.482", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.240", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die erhoffte Effizienzsteigerung im Bereich des Materials erreicht werden kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.520", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "d\u00fcrfte mehr als fraglich sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.280", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Agenda Attraktivit\u00e4t sollte den Soldatenberuf wettbewerbsf\u00e4hig gegen\u00fcber zivilen Arbeitgebern machen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.880", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kitas am Standort, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.440", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine am zivilen Bereich angelehnte Soldatenarbeitszeitverordnung oder aktuell Schwangerschaftsbekleidung und Handtaschen sind Errungenschaften der \u00c4ra von der Leyen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.520", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einer \u00c4ra, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.521", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die der besonderen Natur des Soldatenberufs allerdings in keiner Weise Rechnung tr\u00e4gt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.521", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.522", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich im Ernstfall als Soldat Leib und Leben zu riskieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.522", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.523", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo soll das enden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.523", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.524", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.524", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.525", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denkt man die Ma\u00dfnahmen konsequent zu Ende, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.525", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.526", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die vermeintlich die Attraktivit\u00e4t der Bundeswehr als Arbeitgeber erh\u00f6hen sollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.526", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.527", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4re dies doch ein individuelles Recht auf K\u00fcndigung des Dienstverh\u00e4ltnisses im Verteidigungsfall. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.527", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.528", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer aber glaubt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.528", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.529", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf diese Weise die Bundeswehr leistungsf\u00e4hig machen zu k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.529", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.530", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der irrt sich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.530", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.531", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was sollte denn den Soldatenberuf attraktiv machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.531", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.532", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn nicht der Respekt vor dem pflichtbewussten B\u00fcrger in Uniform, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.532", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.533", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der f\u00fcr die Gew\u00e4hrleistung der Werte einer freiheitlich-demokratischen Grundordnung bereit ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.533", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.534", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sein Leben einzusetzen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.534", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.535", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Herr Hofreiter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.535", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.536", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben doch noch nicht einmal eine Kaserne von innen gesehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.536", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.537", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD fordert deshalb eine weitere und neue Trendwende, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.537", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.538", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich die Trendwende Respekt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.538", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.539", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Hofreiter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.539", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.540", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu muss sich am Sozialprestige der Soldaten massiv etwas \u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.540", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.541", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das beginnt zum Beispiel im Sozialkundeunterricht an unseren Schulen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.541", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.542", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an denen \u00fcbrigens Jugendoffiziere permanent ausgegrenzt werden,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.542", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.543", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und sollte mit einer objektiven Berichterstattung \u00fcber die Bundeswehr einhergehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.543", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.544", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute erzielt doch ein verbeulter Stahlhelm aus dem Zweiten Weltkrieg in irgendeiner Kaserne der Bundeswehr mehr Aufmerksamkeit in den Medien als Eins\u00e4tze zur Rettung und Evakuierung deutscher Staatsb\u00fcrger aus Krisenregionen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.544", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.545", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In den letzten Jahren sind permanent Zeichen gesetzt worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.545", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.546", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Au\u00dfendarstellung der Bundeswehr ist kaum noch geeignet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.546", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.547", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diejenigen f\u00fcr den Dienst in den Streitkr\u00e4ften zu gewinnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.547", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.548", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die unser Land braucht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.548", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.549", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Immer weniger Soldaten lassen sich nach ihrer Dienstzeit als Reservisten gewinnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.549", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.550", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Dienst als Soldat ist eben kein Job wie jeder andere. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.550", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.551", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer unsere Soldaten gr\u00f6\u00dften Risiken aussetzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.551", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.320", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sollte letztendlich mehr zu bieten haben als Kinderbetreuung und Damenhandtaschen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.400", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Soldaten m\u00fcssen sich mit scheinbar unzeitgem\u00e4\u00dfen Werten wie Treue, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.080", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tapferkeit und Ehre identifizieren k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.081", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.081", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.120", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erlauben Sie eine Zwischenfrage oder -bemerkung von Herrn Lambsdorff?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.121", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nein.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.121", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.122", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.122", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.160", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Treue, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.360", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tapferkeit und Ehre sind Werte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.560", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit denen sich Soldaten identifizieren k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.240", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Werte stehen im Mittelpunkt milit\u00e4rischer Tradition. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.160", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber gem\u00e4\u00df dem gerade durch die Ministerin in Kraft gesetzten Traditionserlass soll sich die Bundeswehr haupts\u00e4chlich auf ihre eigenen Traditionen seit 1956 st\u00fctzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.880", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Angeblich soll aber trotzdem die gesamte deutsche Geschichte im Blick behalten werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.320", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit wird die Traditionspflege in ein enges politisches Korsett gezw\u00e4ngt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.760", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Durch Einzelfallentscheidungen soll Traditionsw\u00fcrdiges kenntlich gemacht werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.960", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um f\u00fcr Handlungssicherheit zu sorgen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.040", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Widerspruch in sich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.160", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Letztendlich war es doch das mangelnde Vertrauen in die Truppe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.760", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "welches zu diesem Neuerlass gef\u00fchrt hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.200", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einzelf\u00e4lle wie der des Franco A. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.760", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wurden als typisch f\u00fcr die Bundeswehr dargestellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.240", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau von der Leyen stellte sich aber nicht vor ihre Soldaten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.240", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern bezichtigte diese pauschal eines Haltungsproblems und allgegenw\u00e4rtiger F\u00fchrungsschw\u00e4che."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.280", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mangelndes Vertrauen f\u00fchrt aber zu einer Einschr\u00e4nkung des Handlungsspielraums der Truppe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.920", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verrechtlichung hat die gerade im milit\u00e4rischen Kontext so wichtige Entscheidungsfreude verdr\u00e4ngt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.000", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Administration ersetzt F\u00fchrung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.440", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Truppe herrschen zunehmend Verunsicherung und Vertrauensverlust."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.600", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere Soldaten durch alle R\u00e4nge verdienen unseren Respekt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.440", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere Achtung und vor allem auch unser Vertrauen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.920", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotz widrigster Bedingungen und nicht selten ohne politische R\u00fcckendeckung leisten sie engagiert ihren Dienst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.921", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Elan und guter Wille \u00fcberbr\u00fccken dabei h\u00e4ufig M\u00e4ngel in Ausr\u00fcstung und Organisation. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.921", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.922", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr junge Soldaten ist das ein \u00c4rgernis; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.922", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.923", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Altgediente resignieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.923", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.924", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind die Folgen der Politik einer Ministerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.924", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.925", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die \u00fcberall Flagge zeigen will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.925", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.926", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "demn\u00e4chst auch noch im Irak, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.926", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.927", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl sie weder die Materiallage noch die Personallage in den Griff bekommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.927", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.928", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber st\u00e4ndig von Trendwenden fabuliert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.928", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.929", 
   "id": "s000118", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Trotz des Scheiterns verbohrt auf angebliche Erfolge zu verweisen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.929", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.930", 
   "id": "s000119", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "widerspricht allerdings fundamentalen milit\u00e4rischen F\u00fchrungsprinzipien."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.930", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.931", 
   "id": "s000120", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eigensinn"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.931", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.932", 
   "id": "s000121", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0so der gro\u00dfe preu\u00dfische Milit\u00e4rreformer Carl von Clausewitz\u00a0\u2013"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.932", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.933", 
   "id": "s000122", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist kein Fehler des Verstandes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.933", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.960", 
   "id": "s000123", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er ist ein Fehler des Gem\u00fcts. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.640", 
   "id": "s000124", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Unbeugsamkeit des Willens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.160", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Reizbarkeit gegen fremde Einrede haben ihren Grund nur in einer besonderen Art von Selbstsucht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.920", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.680", 
   "id": "s000127", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er h\u00e4tte die heutige Verteidigungsministerin nicht besser beschreiben k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.760", 
   "id": "s000128", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich danke Ihnen f\u00fcr Ihre Aufmerksamkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.000", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort zu einer Kurzintervention hat der Kollege Graf Lambsdorff."
   ]
  }
 ]
}